  16,29,"And it will also be said to them So enter the gates of Hell to abide therein! Evil indeed is the lodging the abode of the arrogant."
  16,30,"And it is said to those who fear idolatry ‘What has your Lord revealed?’ They will say ‘Good! For those who were virtuous by embracing faith in this world there will be a virtuous reward namely a goodly life; and truly the abode of the Hereafter that is Paradise is better than the world and all that is in it. God says the following regarding it And truly excellent is the abode of the God-fearing it the Hereafter is."
